title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Volanta - version 1.4
description:
In this video we will have a look at the latest version of Volanta. In this new version several new handy features have been added both for the non-premium and premium users including a really nice enhancement to the Simbrief integration.

If you want to give Volanta a try download it via the link below:
